(1) the payment out of money provided by Parliament of—


(a) any sums so payable under any provision of the Act authorising the Secretary of State to defray or contribute towards the expenses of any scientific authority established under the Act;

(b) the expenses of any government department in respect of the administration of the Act;

(c) any increase attributable to the Act in the sums so payable under any other Act;
